{{Quote|For dessert, Zucca Fruit Pastries. No common zucca meat, get a wild boar. I'd say you could go buy some, but Jabba won't eat something we paid for.|[[Porcellus/Legends|Porcellus]]|<ref name="SWG:JPP">{{SWGcite|exp=NGE|type=general|Jabba's Palace : Porcellus|Tatooine}}</ref>}}
'''Zucca fruit pastries''' were a dessert made from the meat of [[zucca boar]]s and fruits. When [[Porcellus/Legends|Porcellus]] made zucca fruit pastries for his master, [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba Desilijic Tiure]], he preferred the more flavorful meat of wild zucca boars.<ref name="SWG:JPP" />

